commentTextItems.html: and the Kiwis show that the latest form of "underhand" tactics from Australia will not prevent their entry into the super 6. Cairns lofting it out of the ground over the forward square leg, a super 6 for the super 6

commentPostTextItems.html: Pakistan finish 1st, Australia 2nd, New Zealand 3rd. The 1st Super 6 match on July 4th will be India v Australia. Australia have announced that SRT doesn't have to bat, they will just give him the 100 to save time.

Asim Butt has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (5) for SCOT, going past John Blain
